<!DOCTYPE task PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Task//EN" "task.dtd" []>
<task xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" id="changing-external-related-link-into-external-related-link-to-existing-document" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="urn:oasis:names:tc:dita:xsd:task.xsd:1.1">
  <title>Changing External Related Link into External Related Link to Existing Document</title>
  <taskbody>
    <context>
      <p>To select a new target for an external related link   from existing documents, do the following:</p>
    </context>
    <steps>
      <step conref="changing-the-target-of-local-related-link.xml#changing-the-target-of-local-related-link/place-cursor-in-related-link">
        <cmd/>
      </step>
      <step id="step-call-change-external-related-link-dialog">
        <cmd>Call up the <uicontrol>Change External Related Link Dialog</uicontrol>.</cmd>
        <info>
          <p>To call up the <keyword>Change External Related Link Dialog</keyword>, choose <menucascade>
              <uicontrol>DITA</uicontrol>
              <uicontrol>Insert External Related Link</uicontrol>
            </menucascade> or click the <uicontrol>Insert External Related Link</uicontrol> button <image href="insert-external-related-link-button.png" align="center"/> on the toolbar.</p>
        </info>
      </step>
      <step conref="changing-local-related-link-into-external-related-link-to-existing-document.xml#changing-local-related-link-into-external-related-link-to-existing-document/specify-file">
        <cmd/>
      </step>
      <step conref="changing-local-related-link-into-external-related-link-to-existing-document.xml#changing-local-related-link-into-external-related-link-to-existing-document/specify-target">
        <cmd/>
      </step>
      <step conref="inserting-external-related-link-to-existing-document.xml#inserting-external-related-link-to-existing-document/specify-attributes-related-link">
        <cmd/>
      </step>
      <step conref="changing-the-target-of-local-related-link.xml#changing-the-target-of-local-related-link/change-related-link">
        <cmd/>
      </step>
      <step conref="changing-the-target-of-local-xref.xml#changing-the-target-of-local-xref/step-close-dialog-on-change">
        <cmd/>
      </step>
    </steps>
  </taskbody>
</task>
